OL,3,COver half of drivers say litter on
OL,4,CSouth East roads is getting worse
OL,6,FLittering on roads in the South East
OL,7,Fis getting worse, according to
OL,8,FBasingstoke-based The AA.
OL,10,FThe Automobile Association has carried
OL,11,Fout a poll of 11,000 members across
OL,12,Fthe UK and more than half (55%) said
OL,13,Fthey notice more rubbish on roads and
OL,14,Fsurrounding areas than in the past.
OL,16,FThat is compared with 52% who said the
OL,17,Fsame thing in a survey conducted in
OL,18,FMay last year.
