OL,3,COver half of drivers say litter on
OL,4,CSouth East roads is getting worse
OL,6,FEdmund King, director of the AA
OL,7,FCharitable Trust, described the
OL,8,Ffigures as "a wake-up call" and
OL,9,Fdeclared it is "time to resolve the
OL,10,Flitter problem once and for all".
OL,12,FThe poll, conducted last month,
OL,13,Frevealed 55% of those surveyed felt
OL,14,Fthere was more litter in the South
OL,15,FEast compared to last year (52%).
OL,17,FThe West Midlands is the UK's worst
OL,18,Fregion for having more litter on
OL,19,Froads, with 63% of respondents
OL,20,Freporting an increase.
