OL,3,COver half of drivers say litter on
OL,4,CSouth East roads is getting worse
OL,6,FThat was followed by 58% in the North
OL,7,FEast, and 57% in both eastern England
OL,8,Fand the Yorkshire/Humberside area.
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland had the lowest
OL,11,Fpercentage of respondents who believe
OL,12,Froad littering is more prevalent, at
OL,13,F49%.
OL,15,FThe AA recommended local authorities
OL,16,Fshould be given greater funding to
OL,17,Fsupport enforcement of vehicle
OL,18,Foccupants who drop litter, and clean-
OL,19,Fup operations.
