OL,3,COver half of drivers say litter on
OL,4,CSouth East roads is getting worse
OL,6,FIt also called for investment in
OL,7,Froadside infrastructure such as larger
OL,8,Fand more prominent bins at lay-bys and
OL,9,Fservice stations, to make it easier
OL,10,Ffor drivers to dispose of waste
OL,11,Fproperly.
OL,13,FMr King said: "There is no excuse for
OL,14,Fcar litter louts. Tossing rubbish from
OL,15,Fvehicles spoils the environment, costs
OL,16,Fmillions and puts road workers' lives
OL,17,Fat risk when they must clear up.
