OL,3,COver half of drivers say litter on
OL,4,CSouth East roads is getting worse
OL,6,F"It is astonishing the number of
OL,7,Fplastic bottles, take-away wrappers
OL,8,Fand even kitchen sinks discarded at
OL,9,Fthe roadside. The rise in public
OL,10,Fconcern about roadside litter is a
OL,11,Fwake-up call."
OL,13,FJohn Read, founder of the Clean Up
OL,14,FBritain campaign, said: "The data
OL,15,Fconfirms what many of us see every day
OL,16,F- litter is getting worse, and it's
OL,17,Fdamaging our environment and our
OL,18,Fcommunities.
OL,20,F"We need to treat this as a national
OL,21,Femergency.
